content.description:
DRL Deluxe starts at the bottom of the cave feature, start on the lowest undercling, powerful moves up to good holds lead you to the V6 variation (described below).  

  Follow the cave out and top out the very high V3 finish. 

V6 Variation: Start at the second highest undercling, right foot on a knob and left uses a toe hook on the start hold of the V9. Fire off powerful moves to the top out. 

V3 Variation: Stand start at the head height jug.
content.protection: A lot of pads and people who know how to spot well.

content.description:
The Upper Outfromunder Boulder exists just a short walk up in the gully towards the Butte Proper from The Outfromunder Boulder (aka The Cube). 

  This boulder holds a lot of mega lines, high ball, powerful routes. With room for some new develop to still be had. Don't be deceived by your perceived landing zone in this area, the vortexes of thumb butte exist here and you will fall off balance and to the right of everything you are climbing on. This is not a joke.
